strings: <voice_0x0100154A><se_def>awesome!: People and women! The high priest is dead. Our prayers with him...
<voice_0x0100154B><se_def>awesome!: He sits next to Devi now. Someone tried to twist the circumstances of her death...
<voice_0x0100154C><se_def>awesome!: But it can be guaranteed that the cause of death was a natural cause.
<voice_0x0100154D><se_def>awesome!: So, let me tell you!
<voice_0x0100154E><se_def>awesome!: I am no longer a high priest!
<voice_0x0100154F><se_def>awesome!: No, I don't want to be a useless idol any more, I must admit!
<voice_0x01001550><se_def>awesome!: ask who the king is
<voice_0x01001551><se_def>awesome!: Only a king was born to a righteous family!
<voice_0x01001552><se_def>awesome!: Doesn't that give you the right to do anything you want? I moved my legs and waited. But no one answered! ??
<voice_0x01001553><se_def>awesome!: The soldier is demanding this behavior, which is highly unacceptable!
<voice_0x01001554><se_def>awesome!: Ascending to the Throne This warrior never escaped the social class he was born into.
<voice_0x01001555><se_def>awesome!: I'm just a soldier! My son kicked me out of the house! A common person like me is not qualified to be the high priest!
<voice_0x01001556><se_def>awesome!: The Church believes this. say yes These positions of responsibility are occupied only by incompetent nobles!
<voice_0x01001557><se_def>awesome!: Our great, great and true holiness! He has it all! ???
<voice_0x01001558><se_def>awesome!: Prayers for an uncertain world Perhaps...but not yet!
<voice_0x01001559><se_def>awesome!: Our high priest, our king, our goddess They ruled us from their throne! Certainly worthless!
<voice_0x0100155A><se_def>awesome!: ...I'm different
<voice_0x0100155B><se_def>awesome!: because in my blood there is not a trace of grace
<voice_0x0100155C><se_def>awesome!: I'm still here! temp worker!
<voice_0x0100155D><se_def>awesome!: Follow! It's time to fire stupid managers and elect new managers!
<voice_0x0100155E><se_def>awesome!: This is also the reason...
<voice_0x0100155F><se_def>awesome!: You have the potential, follow me...
<voice_0x01001560><se_def>awesome!: Or join these invaders and fulfill your destiny!
No sound. the
<voice_0x01001561>If you want to use the editor!
The little ghost pilot says "<hero>"!
<voice_0x01001562><se_def>awesome!: I have to go!
<voice_0x01001563><se_def>awesome!: But if you come between me and my destiny
<voice_0x01001564><se_def>awesome!: you gave me a chance
